{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"33344448ba","title":"“污蔑革命领袖”的言论","origin":"中共厦门大学委员会宣传部编印《右派反动言论集》，1957年9月20日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ef0681985b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"33344448ba"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"058bf3ad7c","name":"厦门大学"},{"id":"65ecdea048","name":"郑朝宗"},{"id":"a294034bc6","name":"张良玉"},{"id":"db3b13f480","name":"张鸣镛"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"098a00bcd5","type":"title","text":"“污蔑革命领袖”的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"0540bd574e","type":"authors","text":"厦门大学郑朝宗张良玉张鸣镛","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"1694108664","type":"paragraph","text":"郑朝宗：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"f1456aaacd","type":"paragraph","text":"“大家称赞毛主席是中国第一才子，但其文章在中央政治局却被修改得‘体无完肤’。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"ad59f3656e","type":"paragraph","text":"“此次运动全国不知有多少权威在骂毛主席这个老头子太多事。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"26f3685390","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们离北京远，所以很尊崇毛主席；那些在北京和毛共事的人，也会觉得这老太婆没有什么了不起。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"46a01726ef","type":"paragraph","text":"郑朝宗对李拓之说：“应该把会上哭声录音，转播到北京给毛主席听。”言下之意：肃反残酷，毛主席是个大官僚主义者。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"245986726e","type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席文章写得比别人好，是因为他有情报。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"ea3509d13c","type":"paragraph","text":"“你说我讲人家的背后话，毛主席也会讲人家的背后话！”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"e296a399a0","type":"paragraph","text":"“中国为什么没有个人崇拜，毛主席不犯斯大林的错误？因为毛主席读过许多中国旧书，懂得‘中庸之道’。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"3ca1d3a147","type":"paragraph","text":"“郭沫若歌颂毛主席的诗，读起来很肉麻。”(厦大快报5期)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"a10fec2d83","type":"paragraph","text":"化学系张良玉：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"650ade227c","type":"paragraph","text":"“毛泽东选集没有什么新鲜，都是从别人的著作中抄来的。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"9fbef98fe6","type":"paragraph","text":"“中国革命史是夸大，事实上，抗日是蒋介石领导的，蒋介石有一套，共产党当时根本没有什么东西。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"bb0064d445","type":"paragraph","text":"“如果国共和谈，蒋介石回到大陆，那么中国革命史就要改，就不能再悔辱人家。”(厦大快报2期)","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"db394b8f19","type":"paragraph","text":"“毛泽东选集是搬来的，没有新内容”，“正确处理人民内部矛盾没有什么东西。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"718d6a00f8","type":"paragraph","text":"“念马列主义是念教条。”“我拥护马列主义，但反对共产党。”(化三油印)","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"a988ff8329","type":"paragraph","text":"张鸣镛：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"e1747c342d","type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席的理论不够完备，我创造性地发展了马列主义，矛盾不只两种，应该是三种，即敌、我、友。”“台湾蒋介石”是“友”。(厦大快报17期)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"75d9f689d8","type":"paragraph","text":"黄席棠：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"6e1dff38b0","type":"paragraph","text":"1956年夏，汪德耀向高教部设法争取到观礼券，邀黄参加五一观礼(见毛主席)，黄冷笑说：“五一节有什么，毛主席有什么好看？还不如去看高怀蓉”(按：高怀蓉是黄的爱人)！","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"8fad412c41","type":"paragraph","text":"1955年高怀蓉为刘少奇参观清华大学时讲解过实验感到荣幸，高写信告黄，黄冷笑“这有什么值得高兴呢？！要是我的话，我就不理这些。”又说“在国民党时代，我就是这样的人”","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"},{"id":"9bf71b37fc","type":"paragraph","text":"1957年在课堂上对同学说：北京的g(重力加速度)比厦门g大并不是毛主席在那边的缘故。”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba"}],"page":{"id":"dadf682352","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"33344448ba","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}